name: Medicine Man by Cory Van Lew

metadata.name: Kambo 100/300
metadata.description: Depicting his spiritual experience with a medicinal ritual among the indigenous Amazonian peoples, Kambo was crafted by renowned artist Cory Van Lew. The image includes Van Lew wrapped in a blanket while in a trance, lying on a large rock by a river, experiencing a state of bliss.
